high_descs: Turn right and step forward to face the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Take a step to the left to face the sink.
Cut the potato in the sink into slices.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the stove.
Place the knife in the pot on the stove.
Turn around and walk forward to face the sink.
Pick up a slice of potato in the sink.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the stove.
Place the potato slice in the pot with the knife.
Pick up the pot with the knife and potato slice in it.
Turn around and step forward to face the center table.
Place the pot on the center table.
anns.task_desc: To put a knife plus a potato slice in a pot as well as place it on the center table.

high_descs: Turn and go to the counter to the right of the sink.
Pick up the knife that is on the counter to the right of the plant.
Turn and go to the sink with the knife in your hand.
Slice the potato that is in the center of the sink with the knife in your hand.
With the knife in hand turn and go to the stove.
Place the knife in your hand in the pot on the front right of the stove on the right side of the pot.
Turn and go to the sink
Pick up a slice of potato that is in the center of the sink. Pick the slice closest to you
With the slice of potato in hand turn and go to the stove.
Place the potato slice in the pan that is on the front right burner. Place the slice of potato to the left of the knife in the pan.
Pick up the pan that is on the front right burner with the knife and potato slice in it.
Turn and go to the island counter to the part directly across from the fridge.
Place the pan on the counter to the right of the tomato and in front of the tea pot.
anns.task_desc: Slice potato and put pan and potato on counter with knife.

high_descs: Turn to the left and approach the counter.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Turn left and go to the sink.
Cut the potato in the sink.
Turn around and go to the stove.
Put the knife in the pot on the stove.
Turn around and head back to the sink.
Pick up a slice of potato from the sink.
Turn around and head back to the stove.
Put the slice of potato in the pot on the stove.
Pick up the pot with the slice of potato and knife in it.
Turn around, go halfway across the room and turn left towards the counter.
Put the pot on the counter to the right of the tomato.
anns.task_desc: Put a slice of potato and knife inside a pot on the counter.
